title: Bright & Spacious Top-Floor Retreat near Hornsey
description:
We are delighted to present to you this exquisite top-floor apartment, nestled within the timeless charm of a Victorian terraced house. Perched high above the cityscape, this stunning abode exudes an air of elegance and sophistication, offering a sanctuary of modern comfort and style.

Step into the heart of this luminous retreat, where a seamless blend of contemporary design and classic architecture awaits. The spacious separate kitchen/living room beckons with its inviting ambiance, bathed in natural light streaming through large windows. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or unwinding after a long day, this versatile space offers the perfect backdrop for both relaxation and entertainment.

Indulge in the luxury of the tiled bathroom, where every detail has been meticulously curated to evoke a sense of tranquility and refinement. From the sleek fixtures to the pristine surfaces, this sanctuary promises a spa-like experience that will rejuvenate both body and mind.

Retreat to the comfort of the double bedroom, where plush carpets and ample storage space create a haven of serenity and rest. As day turns into night, sink into the embrace of luxurious linens and drift off to sleep enveloped in a cocoon of comfort.

This exceptional flat comes fully unfurnished, allowing you the freedom to personalize and design your ideal living space according to your unique style and preferences. Whether you're envisioning a minimalist retreat or a cozy haven filled with eclectic charm, the possibilities are endless.

Conveniently situated mere moments from Hornsey station and Crouch Hill station, commuting to the heart of the city has never been easier. With seamless access to public transportation, you'll enjoy effortless connectivity to all corners of London, ensuring that every adventure is within reach.

Venture just a two-minute stroll away, and you'll find yourself immersed in a vibrant tapestry of local amenities. From charming cafes to boutique shops, everything you need for daily living is right at your doorstep, making convenience a way of life.

Embrace the opportunity to experience the epitome of urban living in this stunning top-floor apartment. With its unrivaled location, exquisite design, and unparalleled comfort, this is a place where every moment is infused with joy, beauty, and possibility.

title: Mordern 2 Bed Flat With Balcony In East London
description:
Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living at City View Point, where luxury and convenience come together in perfect harmony. Situated on the Upper Ground floor of this brand-new development, this spacious two-bedroom apartment offers an exceptional living experience with a host of outstanding features.

As you step into this ground-floor apartment, you'll immediately appreciate the meticulous attention to detail that has gone into every aspect of its design. The living space is in excellent condition and boasts an abundance of natural light, thanks to its dual aspect windows that frame picturesque views of the surrounding area.

The heart of this home is the open-plan reception room, where you can unwind, entertain, and enjoy quality time with friends and family. Whether it's a cozy night in or a lively gathering, this space accommodates it all. The modern kitchen, seamlessly integrated into the living area, is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, making meal preparation a pleasure.

The apartment features two generously sized double bedrooms, each offering a comfortable and tranquil retreat. The second bedroom has been thoughtfully furnished with a double bed and mattress, along with two mirror cupboards, providing ample storage space for your belongings.

The sleek family bathroom is a testament to contemporary design, showcasing modern fittings and elegant finishes. It's the perfect place to rejuvenate after a long day or prepare for the day ahead.

What sets this apartment apart is its versatility. The living room is tastefully furnished with a dining table and four chairs, and a neutral-colored sofa that can be transformed into a comfortable sleeping sofa bed when needed, accommodating guests with ease. 

Step outside onto your private terrace, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or unwind in the evening while taking in the serene views of the River Lea. For an elevated experience, residents also have access to a shared rooftop terrace, a perfect spot to soak in the panoramic city vistas.

City View Point is more than just a stylish apartment; it's a lifestyle. The development is strategically located, offering close proximity to a wide array of amenities, ensuring that your daily needs, from shopping to dining, are met effortlessly. For those who prefer an eco-friendly commute, there's a shared bicycle storage room on-site, catering to cycling enthusiasts.

Transportation is a breeze with easy access to the Blackwall Tunnel and Langdon Park DLR Station, making it a great choice for commuters. The location offers the perfect balance of convenience and tranquility, with the bustling city at your doorstep and the River Lea as your peaceful backdrop.

Experience the best in contemporary urban living at City View Point. This apartment is more than just a home; it's a reflection of your modern lifestyle and a testament to your commitment to quality living. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your own.

title: Nice Room Next The River!
description:
Welcome to this cosy double room located in Homerton, with the convenient postcode: E9 5PJ, close to Hackney Central, Clapton, Hackney Wick and Stratford.
Available on the 5th of November and it’s for single individuals. 

ROOM
This room is fully furnished with a comfortable double bed, a wardrobe, a chest of drawers, a bedside table, a bookcase, a large mirror, a desk and chair, a pair of black-out curtains, and an LCD Smart TV. 
Your privacy is assured with designated areas in the bathroom, kitchen and fridge/freezer, along with your own room key.

FLAT
A fully equipped 4-bedroom flat, all on one floor, awaits you with cool and friendly flatmates.
The kitchen is full kitchen equipment, also features a washing machine for your convenience.
Additional essentials such as iron, ironing board, hoover, mop, and hanging dryers are readily available.
Enjoy free high-speed broadband internet.
FREE TWICE A WEEK CLEANING SERVICE ensures the common areas, including the kitchen, bathrooms, and corridors, remain clean and tidy. 
Additionally, complimentary cleaning products such as hand wash soap, washing up liquid, sponges, and cloths are provided regularly.

PRICE & CONTRACT
Rent is £850 per month.
A one-month deposit is required. 
No agency fees. 
All bills are included (Electricity and gas included up to a specified budget depending on the month). 

Long Term Discount: £20 off on monthly rent for 10 months contract (Your saving: £200).

TRANSPORT & AREA
Homerton is a trendy area with plenty of cool coffee shops and pubs, making it a lively place to
live. Nearby Hackney Wick offers even more choices for dining out and enjoying the nightlife.
You'll find the beautiful River Lea just a minute's walk away and Hackney Marshes within a 5
minute stroll. Plus, there's a supermarket right across the street for your convenience.

Local Attractions
Take a 10-minute walk to Chatsworth Road for its charming markets and cozy cafes. Homerton
Hospital is also within walking distance, providing peace of mind.
If you're in the mood for fun, Hackney Wick is a 15-minute walk away, while Stratford and
Westfield Shopping Centre are just a 20-minute stroll. And for fitness buffs, Kings Hall Leisure
Centre is a 20-minute walk, offering a great gym and swimming pool.

Transport Links
Getting around is easy with Homerton Station and Hackney Wick Station both a 10-15 minute walk
or a quick 5-minute bus ride away. These stations connect you to Stratford, Westfield Shopping
Centre, Hackney Central, and Dalston, as well as direct lines to Highbury & Islington, Richmond,
and Clapham Junction.

Bus Services
Bus stops are just a few minutes' walk from the flat, with night buses available for late-night travel.
Hop on the W15, 236, 276, 308, 26, or 242 for easy access to various parts of the city.

Don't miss this great opportunity! Contact us today to schedule your viewing.
